  "name": "Anti-Life Shell",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg",
  "system": {
    "description": "<p>This spell creates a mobile, 20 ft. diameter, sphere of energy around the caster that prevents the entrance of animals, aberrations, beasts, magical beasts, dragons, fey, giants, humanoids, oozes, plants, shapechangers and vermin; but not constructs, elementals, outsiders or undead. The shell is transparent, but it is not invisible. It moves with the caster. This spell may be used only defensively, not aggressively; an attempt to force the shell against a creature normally kept at bay causes the shell to collapse.</p>",
